Buildfiles to install the initial build environment

cross-* : Cross-Toolchain (See Chapter 5)
temp-*  : Temporary tools (See Chapter 6)

lfs.chroot : Sets up the chroot to all installation of LFS proper
lfs.config : Default configuration file
lfs.stage1 : Setup environment, and install the cross-* and temp-* tools
lfs.stage2 : Additional temporary tools that must be built under chroot
stage1.lfsbuild : Meta package with list of required build scripts
stage2.lfsbuild : Meta package with list of required build scripts

template.lfsbuild : Template for lfs build scripts